OL,7,FThe energy price cap will rise by #35
OL,8,Fa year from Wednesday for a typical
OL,9,Fhousehold in England, Scotland and
OL,10,FWales.
OL,12,FThe changes come as the weather cools
OL,13,Fand many people switch on their
OL,14,Fcentral heating, putting more pressure
OL,15,Fon household finances.
