OL,7,FThe energy bill for the average
OL,8,Fhousehold will rise by 2% on
OL,9,FWednesday, October 1 in England,
OL,10,FScotland and Wales.
OL,12,FThe increase in energy costs comes
OL,13,Fdespite wholesale prices falling by 2%
OL,14,Fover the three months before Ofgem's
OL,15,Flatest price cap decision.
OL,17,FHow will it affect my bills?
OL,19,FHouseholds paying by direct debit for
OL,20,Fgas and electricity will see their
OL,21,Fbills go from #1,720 a year to #1,755.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
