OL,7,FThat's an increase of #35 a year.
OL,9,FDebt charity StepChange says while the
OL,10,Fincrease "seems like a small amount",
OL,11,Fit has noticed a rise in households
OL,12,Fstruggling to pay their bills.
OL,14,FThe charity reported a 32% increase in
OL,15,Faverage energy arrears among its
OL,16,Fclients seeking debt advice over the
OL,17,Flast two years.
