OL,5,Cdown
OL,7,FThe standing charges for electricity
OL,8,Fare set to rise by 4%.
OL,10,FGas is also set to increase by 14% -
OL,11,Fthat's around 7p per day.
OL,13,FStanding charges are the amount
OL,14,Fconsumers pay a day to have energy
OL,15,Fsupplied to their homes.
OL,17,FThe increases are primarily driven by
OL,18,Fthe government's expansion of the Warm
OL,19,FHome Discount.
