OL,7,FConsumer group Which? has urged
OL,8,Fhouseholds still on a standard energy
OL,9,Ftariff to submit a meter reading as
OL,10,Fsoon as possible.
OL,12,FSuppliers who have not received meter
OL,13,Freadings base their bills on estimated
OL,14,Fusage, meaning households could be
OL,15,Foverpaying, while others may not be
OL,16,Fpaying enough.
OL,18,FThey also suggest shopping around.
