OL,7,F"As a rule of thumb, we'd recommend
OL,8,Flooking for deals cheaper than the
OL,9,Fcurrent price cap, not longer than 12
OL,10,Fmonths and without significant exit
OL,11,Ffees," Which? Energy editor Emily
OL,12,FSeymour said.
OL,14,FMore than 6 million low-income
OL,15,Fhouseholds are also eligible to
