OL,7,FEnergy regulator Ofgem said the latest
OL,8,Fincrease was driven by electricity
OL,9,F"balancing costs" incurred by network
OL,10,Foperators.
OL,12,FIt ensures a stable electricity supply
OL,13,Ffor when there is both too much power
OL,14,Fand too little power in the system,
OL,15,Fadding around #1.23 a month to the
OL,16,Faverage household bill.
OL,18,FOther factors include costs associated
OL,19,Fwith the extension of the government's
OL,20,FWarm Home Discount scheme.JWhere can I
OL,21,Fgo for help?
