OL,12,FWhat is the energy cap?
OL,14,FThe energy price cap, regulated by
OL,15,FOfgem, restricts the amount that
OL,16,Fenergy suppliers can charge for each
OL,17,Funit of gas and electricity and covers
OL,18,Faround two-thirds of homes in the UK.
